{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b4eb05e874","title":"给文脉昌的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"258095b20b","index":0,"year":1915,"month":2,"day":24,"articleId":"b4eb05e874"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji1","name":"毛泽东全集第1卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5be2a94ac4","type":"paragraph","text":"给文脉昌的信”（1915年2月24日）","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"b4eb05e874"},{"id":"c5c0766f73","type":"paragraph","text":"苹业森昌光四森昌光","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"b4eb05e874"},{"id":"2de2c08227","type":"paragraph","text":"美菜成世危言增订新编","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"b4eb05e874"},{"id":"8bbfab3c9e","type":"paragraph","text":"一茶","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"b4eb05e874"},{"id":"f17eff260a","type":"paragraph","text":"节主发","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"b4eb05e874"},{"id":"52a96d9299","type":"paragraph","text":"文任1915年，毛泽东向表兄文咏昌归还的《盛世危言》和还书便条。[1]这是毛泽东写的一张还书便来。原无写作年份，据文味昌在新中国成立初期回忆，这张便条是“民四年”（即1915年）毛泽东从湖南省立第一师范学校回家过春节时所写。所署“正月十一日”系农历，公历为2月24日。咏昌先生：书十一本，内《盛世危言》以失布阻，《新民从报》损去首叶，","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"b4eb05e874"},{"id":"14cc69928f","type":"paragraph","text":"泽东敬白","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"b4eb05e874"},{"id":"9ed79d01af","type":"paragraph","text":"正月十一日又国文教科[书]二本，信一封[]咏品，即文水昌（1884-1961），名昌，又写作润昌、运昌，湖南湘乡唐家托（今属油潭市山区大坪乡）人，毛泽东的表兄。2]《盛世危言》，清末郑观应（1842-1921）著。书名及内容编排层责洋务源学习西方教术而不从事本国政治改革，是“遗共体而求共用”“透其说，他少年时阅读此书，“非常喜欢”。[3]《新民丛报》半月刊，景启起主编，1902年创刊于日本横滨。初期","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"b4eb05e874"}],"page":{"id":"06fecdede1","publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"b4eb05e874","start":169,"end":170}}}},"__N_SSG":true}